<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Lemonade Recipe</title>
</head>

<body>
    <h1>Lemonade Recipe</h1>
    <h2>Ingredients</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>2 fresh lemons</li>
        <li>2 cups cold water</li>
        <li>2 tablespoons sugar</li>
        <li>Pinch of salt</li>
        <li>Ice cubes</li>
        <li>Mint leaves (optional)</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Steps to Prepare</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Cut the lemons and squeeze the juice into a glass</li>
        <li>Add sugar and salt to the lemon juice</li>
        <li>Pour in cold water and mix well</li>
        <li>Add ice cubes</li>
        <li>Garnish with mint leaves</li>
        <li>Serve chilled </li>
    </ol>
    </body>
</html>
